Used to administer:
General ops (emails), surveys, shared files

Collected data:
Email addresses, names, other client information

Data trashing policy:
Emails forwarded into Basecamp are deleted after 1 year of receiving.

Service privacy policy:
See this page. (https://basecamp.com/about/policies/privacy)

